        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Contained within this small glass tube is a twisted wire filament crackling with electricity, sending static prickling through the hair of anyone holding it. The spell DC of any spell cast by activating this item is 17. \n* **Armor** You gain resistance 2 to electricity.\n* **Weapon** After you cast an electricity spell by activating the coil, your Strikes with the weapon deal an additional 1d4 electricity damage until the end of your next turn.",
